  "title": "Smelting Sand in Blast Furnace",
  "description": "Smelt Sand Faster in the Blast Furnace",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a><h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B2v72Ff.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/smelting-sand-in-blast-furnace\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/451602?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/smelting-sand-in-blast-furnace\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/smelting-sand-in-blast-furnace?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This Minecraft mod makes you able to smelt Sand into Glass in a blast furnace, which means you can smelt Sand at 2x speed.<br />Blast Furnaces are in real-world used to melt sand into glass so it would make sense if it was the same in Minecraft.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aqTJhBa.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"364\" height=\"267\"/></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/blastingsand.json</code> in your profile folder. Please note that any changes will require restarting Minecraft to take effect.</p>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>sand_list</b> - List of Blocks you can blast into Glass</p></center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>\n",
